     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "Purification[mat] returns a purification of the mixed state described by \
the density matrix mat. Purification[rho, {s1, s2, ...}, {e1, e2, ...}] \
returns a purification of the mixed state described by the density operator \
rho on the system species {s1, s2, ...} by extending the system with the \
environment species {e1, e2, ...}. Purification[rho, {s1, s2, ...}] is \
equivalent to Purification[Matrix[rho, {s1, s2, ...}]] for an expression \
expression rho. Purification[rho] is equivalent to Purification[Matrix[rho]] \
for an expression expression rho.", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, 
